<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Patterns_of_CD.svg" class="image" title="Patterns of CD.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1c/Patterns_of_CD.svg/190px-Patterns_of_CD.svg.png" width="190" height="434" border="0" /></a></div>
