<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;"><small>The three most common sites of intestinal involvement in <b>Crohn's disease</b> are</small>
<p><small><a href="/wiki/Ileum" title="Ileum">ileal</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ileocolic" title="Ileocolic" class="mw-redirect">ileocolic</a> and <a href="/wiki/Colon" title="Colon">colonic</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-Baumgart_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Baumgart-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></small></p>
</td>
