<td><a href="/wiki/Terminal_ileum" title="Terminal ileum">Terminal ileum</a> involvement</td>
<td>Commonly</td>
<td>Seldom</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Colon involvement</td>
<td>Usually</td>
<td>Always</td>
