<td>Seldom</td>
<td>Usually<sup id="cite_ref-Kornbluth-Sachar2004_69-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Kornbluth-Sachar2004-69" title=""><span>[</span>70<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Involvement around the <a href="/wiki/Anus" title="Anus">anus</a></td>
