<li id="cite_note-94"><b><a href="#cite_ref-94" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFTysk_C.2C_Lindberg_E.2C_J.C3.A4rnerot_G.2C_Flod.C3.A9rus-Myrhed_B1988">Tysk C, Lindberg E, Järnerot G, Flodérus-Myrhed B (1988). "<a href="http://gut.bmj.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=3396969" class="external text" title="http://gut.bmj.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=3396969" rel="nofollow">Ulcerative colitis and Crohn's disease in an unselected population of monozygotic and dizygotic twins. A study of heritability and the influence of smoking</a>". <i>Gut</i> <b>29</b> (7): 990–6. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/3396969" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/3396969">PMID 3396969</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>: <a href="http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?tool=pmcentrez&amp;artid=1433769" class="external text" title="http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?tool=pmcentrez&amp;artid=1433769" rel="nofollow">1433769</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://gut.bmj.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=3396969" class="external free" title="http://gut.bmj.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=3396969" rel="nofollow">http://gut.bmj.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=3396969</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Ulcerative+colitis+and+Crohn%27s+disease+in+an+unselected+population+of+monozygotic+and+dizygotic+twins.+A+study+of+heritability+and+the+influence+of+smoking&amp;rft.jtitle=Gut&amp;rft.aulast=Tysk+C%2C+Lindberg+E%2C+J%C3%A4rnerot+G%2C+Flod%C3%A9rus-Myrhed+B&amp;rft.au=Tysk+C%2C+Lindberg+E%2C+J%C3%A4rnerot+G%2C+Flod%C3%A9rus-Myrhed+B&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.volume=29&amp;rft.issue=7&amp;rft.pages=990%E2%80%936&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/3396969&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fgut.bmj.com%2Fcgi%2Fpmidlookup%3Fview%3Dlong%26pmid%